    • Constructor Detail

      • Disciplina

        public Disciplina(java.lang.String nome,
          Modalidade modalidade,
          boolean tipoDisc,
          int genero,
          boolean ordenacao,
          int tipoClass)
        Main constructor of this class.
        Parameters:
        nome - the name of the competition.
        modalidade - the sport of this competition.
        tipoDisc - the type of the competition. If is a team competition, this atribute is True.
        genero - the genre of this competition. If is a male competion, is 0 (zero), if is a female is 1(one) and if is a mixed competition is 2(two).
        ordenacao - the ordination of this competition. If is the highest, who wins, this atribute is true.
        tipoClass - the type of classification of this competition. If is a distance competition, is 0(zero), if is a time competition, is 1(one), if is a score competition, is 2(two) and if is a ranked competition, is 3(three).
